557
00:24:15,760 --> 00:24:19,760
Let's also talk about woff events during

558
00:24:18,240 --> 00:24:22,400
distribution.

559
00:24:19,760 --> 00:24:25,039
First is the preliminary supply. This is

560
00:24:22,400 --> 00:24:27,520
when smart money starts selling after

561
00:24:25,039 --> 00:24:29,679
prices have been going up. the trading

562
00:24:27,520 --> 00:24:31,600
volume increases and the difference

563
00:24:29,679 --> 00:24:34,640
between the highest and the lowest

564
00:24:31,600 --> 00:24:37,600
prices widens. This suggests that the

565
00:24:34,640 --> 00:24:40,080
trend might be changing. Next, we have

566
00:24:37,600 --> 00:24:42,159
the buying climax. During a buying

567
00:24:40,080 --> 00:24:45,039
climax, there is a peak in buying

568
00:24:42,159 --> 00:24:48,080
activity with higher price differences.

569
00:24:45,039 --> 00:24:51,679
A buying climax often marks a top in the

570
00:24:48,080 --> 00:24:54,320
market. Next is the automatic reaction.

571
00:24:51,679 --> 00:24:56,480
After the buying climax, the intense

572
00:24:54,320 --> 00:24:59,200
buying pressure decreases and the

573
00:24:56,480 --> 00:25:01,200
sell-off occurs. This reaction helps

574
00:24:59,200 --> 00:25:04,080
define the lower boundary of the

575
00:25:01,200 --> 00:25:06,720
distribution trading range. Next is the

576
00:25:04,080 --> 00:25:09,360
secondary test. The price revisits the

577
00:25:06,720 --> 00:25:11,919
level of the buying climax to test the

578
00:25:09,360 --> 00:25:14,240
balance between supply and demand. So,

579
00:25:11,919 --> 00:25:16,480
the trading volume and price differences

580
00:25:14,240 --> 00:25:18,480
should decrease as the price approaches

581
00:25:16,480 --> 00:25:22,159
the resistance level of the buying

582
00:25:18,480 --> 00:25:24,880
climax. Sometimes a secondary test takes

583
00:25:22,159 --> 00:25:27,520
the form of an up thrust, a liquidity

584
00:25:24,880 --> 00:25:29,840
run, where the price briefly moves above

585
00:25:27,520 --> 00:25:32,799
the resistance level before quickly

586
00:25:29,840 --> 00:25:35,520
reversing back below it. Next is the

587
00:25:32,799 --> 00:25:38,720
sign of weakness. This is observed as a

588
00:25:35,520 --> 00:25:41,520
downward move to or slightly below the

589
00:25:38,720 --> 00:25:43,679
lower boundary of the trading range. It

590
00:25:41,520 --> 00:25:46,720
usually happens with increased price

591
00:25:43,679 --> 00:25:48,799
differences and increased volume. The

592
00:25:46,720 --> 00:25:51,200
automatic reaction and the sign of

593
00:25:48,799 --> 00:25:54,400
weakness indicate that supply is now

594
00:25:51,200 --> 00:25:56,960
dominant in the market. And finally, we

595
00:25:54,400 --> 00:25:59,440
have the last point of supply. After

596
00:25:56,960 --> 00:26:01,840
testing support on a sign of weakness,

597
00:25:59,440 --> 00:26:04,320
there may be a rally with narrow price

598
00:26:01,840 --> 00:26:07,120
differences. The market struggles to

599
00:26:04,320 --> 00:26:09,600
advance during this rally, indicating a

600
00:26:07,120 --> 00:26:11,279
weak demand.

601
00:26:09,600 --> 00:26:14,400
Now, let's look at the phases of

602
00:26:11,279 --> 00:26:16,960
distribution. In phase A, the prior

603
00:26:14,400 --> 00:26:19,760
uptrend stops and the supply starts

604
00:26:16,960 --> 00:26:23,200
entering the market. We see preliminary

605
00:26:19,760 --> 00:26:25,679
supply and the buying climax followed by

606
00:26:23,200 --> 00:26:29,440
an automatic reaction and a secondary

607
00:26:25,679 --> 00:26:32,159
test of the buying climax. In phase B,

608
00:26:29,440 --> 00:26:35,200
smart money initiate short positions in

609
00:26:32,159 --> 00:26:37,279
anticipation of the next decline. Signs

610
00:26:35,200 --> 00:26:40,080
of weakness are often followed by

611
00:26:37,279 --> 00:26:42,480
significant downward price movements and

612
00:26:40,080 --> 00:26:45,200
increased trading volume.

613
00:26:42,480 --> 00:26:48,240
Phase C is an interesting phase. This is

614
00:26:45,200 --> 00:26:50,880
where up thrusts may occur. Price moves

615
00:26:48,240 --> 00:26:53,840
above the trading range and then sharply

616
00:26:50,880 --> 00:26:56,640
reverses back down. Many retail traders

617
00:26:53,840 --> 00:27:00,559
