676
00:29:35,919 --> 00:29:41,520
out and start buying as well. All these

677
00:29:39,279 --> 00:29:44,640
factors contribute to the professional

678
00:29:41,520 --> 00:29:48,960
traders bullish positions. If you see

679
00:29:44,640 --> 00:29:51,440
any testing or down bars on low volume

680
00:29:48,960 --> 00:29:54,480
after the gapping event, it is

681
00:29:51,440 --> 00:29:56,480
considered a strong buy signal. This

682
00:29:54,480 --> 00:29:59,039
suggests that the market is likely to

683
00:29:56,480 --> 00:30:02,360
